title: 139th Deerfield Fair starts, 1 of oldest in New England
text:
DEERFIELD, N.H. (AP) - The Deerfield Fair, billed as New England' oldest family fair, is starting up for its 139th year.
The fair lasts through Sunday.
Shows this year include vaudeville variety, magic, puppets, a chorus, square dancing, and music.
The Miss Deerfield Fair Pageant is Friday.
